net.proteusframework.data.filesystem

Class TemporaryFileEntity

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.proteusframework.data.filesystem.FileSystemEntity
      • net.proteusframework.data.filesystem.FileEntity
        • net.proteusframework.data.filesystem.TemporaryFileEntity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class TemporaryFileEntity
extends FileEntity
    Temporary FileEntity. You can use this as a placeholder for a File that hasn't been stored as a FileEntity. This can be used with the FileSystemDAO.
    Author:
    Russ Tennant (russ@i2rd.com)
    See Also:
